Interface for the ffmpeg video codec library.
This is a decode only interface for now.

Files:

audiosource.lsh
 -- generic class for accessing audio data.
    (independent from ffmpeg)

videosource.lsh
 -- generic class for accessing video data.
    (independent from ffmpeg)

ffmpeg-config.lsh 
-- configuration file for ffmpeg.

ffmpeg.lsh
-- access to multimedia file via the ffmpeg library.

